<seg id="608">In the CZ, a special financial office for large companies is planned for 2012</seg>
<seg id="609">In Germany, the financial administration does not collect comparably large amounts of data.</seg>
<seg id="610">Accordingly, it is harder to perform these tasks in the same way.</seg>
<seg id="611">The focus is more on selecting relevant individual cases.</seg>
