<seg id="613">Based on the data in VAT pre-registrations or VAT declarations as well as inspection notes select the cases to be examined and ensure the appropriate taxation.</seg>
<seg id="614">Appropriate management processes and risk management systems should be introduced in order to reduce revenue losses at VAT while increasing the risk of being discovered.</seg>
